data.inputSetTemplateYaml:
pipeline:
  identifier: "testPipeline_Cypress"
  stages:
  - stage:
      identifier: "s1"
      type: "Deployment"
      spec:
        serviceConfig:
          serviceDefinition:
            type: "ServerlessAwsLambda"
            spec:
              artifacts:
                primary:
                  type: "AmazonS3"
                  spec:
                    bucketName: "<+input>"
                    filePathRegex: "<+input>"
        infrastructure:
          infrastructureDefinition:
            type: "ServerlessAwsLambda"
            spec:
              connectorRef: "<+input>"
              stage: "<+input>"
              region: "<+input>"
